data.description: Welcome to 2317 S Washington, a beautifully updated home with a spacious backyard and endless potential. This charming property offers a new kitchen and bath, providing a modern and stylish living space for its new owners. The new kitchen is a standout feature, boasting modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space.  The updated bathroom offers a fresh and contemporary design. With its new fixtures and finishes, you'll feel ready to enjoy your new space. One of the highlights of this property is the large backyard, complete with a garden area. Whether you have a green thumb or simply enjoy spending time outdoors, this backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Additionally, there is a bonus room that is ready to be finished by the new buyer. This space can be transformed into a home office, a playroom, or even a guest suite - the choice is yours. Let your imagination run wild and create a space that perfectly suits your needs and lifestyle. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is conveniently situated near schools, parks, shopping centers, and restaurants, ensuring that all your daily needs are within easy reach. Don't miss the opportunity to make this updated and versatile property your own. Schedule a showing today. Let me know if there's anything else I can assist you with!
